##### Damage Type by Class
Damage Type | Class
------------|------
Acid        |Druid
Bludgeoning |
"Chaos"     |Warlock
Cold        |Mage, Shaman
Fire        |Mage, Shaman, Warlock
Force       |Druid (Lunar), Mage
Lightning   |Shaman
Necrotic    |Priest, Warlock
Piercing    |
Poison      |Druid
Psychic     |Priest (Void)
Radiant     |Druid (Solar), Priest
Slashing    |
Thunder     |Shaman

##### Damage/Class
Class   | Damage Type
--------|------------
Druid   | Acid, Force (Lunar), Poison, Radiant (Solar)
Mage    | Cold, Fire, Force
Priest  | Necrotic, Psychic (Void), Radiant
Shaman  | Cold, Fire, Lightning, Thunder
Warlock |"Chaos", Fire, Necrotic

