*1st-level conjuration*
___
- **Casting Time:** 1 bonus action
- **Range:** Self
- **Components:** V
- **Duration:** Instantaneous
___
You briefly blink out of existence, teleporting up to 15 feet to an unoccupied space that you can see.

***At Higher Levels.*** When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 2nd level or higher, the range that you can teleport doubles for each slot level above 1st.

